THE GAME
--------

  'Ti_Coune' (pronounced as 'Tee-coon') is a Workbench game where
you have to help a guy called 'Ti_Coune' so he can get to the
exit, but before that, he has to find a key to unlock a fence that
surrounds the exit...

  To allow Ti_Coune to move, there must be 3 walls and one opening
around him. If there are more than one opening, Ti_Coune gets
confused and he will not move...

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

